Former Arsenal footballer Alex Scott, 38, looked drastically different in a behind-the-scenes photoshoot while getting her hair and makeup done. Showing off a new hairdo, the Football Focus presenter revealed she had chopped off her long locks in favour of a sleek bob. Alex posed for numerous selfies to show off her transformation, captioning her Instagram post: “… Allow me to re-introduce myself “We are calling her Bobbi,” she quipped of her new look in view of her 1.7 million followers this evening. It wasn’t long before Alex’s celeb pals and fans inundated the comments section of her post to compliment her on the haircut. Fellow The One Show star Alex Jones, 45, gushed: “I love it Al x.” Former Countdown host Carol Vorderman, 62, added: “OMG I love her.” Fans also chuckled over Alex comparing herself to SpongeBob SquarePants due to the trim, with one adding: “Looks good..SpongeBo....I get it now.” Another almost mistook Alex for Will Smith’s wife, writing: “I thought it was Jada Pinkett you look amazing xx.”